column1: The persons involved reflects all motorists, however they do not reflect other persons involved unless they were injured or killed.

A collision at an intersection located on a precinct border may appear in the list of intersections of any precinct that shares that intersection,
but will appear in only one precinct list.
Collision location is captured as the nearest intersection.
